resoFacts.basement: Finished, Bath Full, Bedroom, Storage Space, Utility Room

data.description: Where is Jamesburg? It's between North Brunswick and Monroe. This beautiful fully renovated 4 bedroom, 2.5 bath ranch style home offers the perfect blend of comfort and space. Situated on a sprawling land, the property features a gorgeous swimming pool, Sauna, green lawn, spaces deck for party, providing a serene yard space. Property front door faces East South and offers fantastic light. Upon entering, you are greeted in the foyer and are brought to the inviting sun filled living room / dining room space, which offers open space concept yet allows for privacy. The well appointed kitchen offers a eat in space and ideal for culinary enthusiasts and gathering. Views of the backyard will not disappoint. Upon entering the backyard you will enjoy the private patio, perfect for entertaining. Experience the perfect blend of comfort, serenity and convenience in this beautiful ranch style home. Offering a full basement for storage and or finishing for more living space and 2 bedroom. 3 car garage which is accessible from exterior of the  basement. All this and in a great location to be seen. Swimming pool, Sauna and Grill to enjoy in your own home!
